    tmp = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.87 * tmp + 0.93) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.59)))
    v2 = 0.44
    v0 = wp.cos((tmp + wp.exp(v1 + 0.15)))

    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.91) - (tmp + 0.36 + v0 + 0.83)) - tmp)
